    "154474642": {
      "title": "z-Tree Zurich Toolbox for Ready-made Economic experiments",
      "abstract": "z-Tree (Zurich Toolbox for Ready-made Economic Experiments) is a software for developing and conducting economic experiments. The software is stable and allows programming almost any kind of experiments in a short time. In this article, I present the guiding principles behind the software design, its features, and its limitations. Copyright Economic Science Association 2007"
